Class SongDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • application.SongDatabase

  • public class SongDatabase
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class uses javaFX to create a gui for the music DB. It can load from and save to a file.It can add music, modify music, and delete music.
    Author:
    Farrukh Khan
